    public class RegexBuilderMainView
extends SystemConfigInlineView<RegexBuilderMainPresenter>
    Shows the view of Regex builder. This view shows the all the options for generating the regex pattern. This view contains the Regex Tester utility. User can also test the generated regex pattern with the help of this utility.
    Version:
    1.0 $LastChangedDate:$
